@X_Entinity_X wrote:

ActionHandler.java, Client.java, Player.java, NpcHandler.java and Npc.java.

Declare the keys in every single one of those classes, then add the ID’S of the Npc’s in NpcHandler.java DropBones and replace that with the keys, so it’s 100% key drop rate.

Anyway why are you using that Dungeoneering base? it’s horrible.

Realm Of Heroes codes into your files. Unless you want to keep your previous added options:

Copy the codes you’ve CREATED BY YOURSELF and save them in a Notepad file.
After pasted the codes and you can copy the codes you saved and put back in order.

Or just find the codes that are related in Dungeoneering and copy paste into your server like before.
